<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="vague-adj">vague <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /veɪɡ/    美 /veɪɡ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>含糊的；不明确的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>vague idea</strong> / answer 
模糊的想法/含糊的答复</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I usually remember people’s faces but I am often <strong>vague about</strong> their names. 
我通常能记住人们的面孔，但经常记不清他们的名字。</p><footer>人教⑩ – 4</footer></div></div>